        <text>
            <body><p>Ego <persName key="stutzmann_himanis#324599" xml:id="d1e137034" corresp="Manassès de Bar-sur-Seine, évêque de Langres (1179-1193)">Manasses, Dei gratia
                                <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#317574" xml:id="d1e137036" corresp="Langres (Haute-Marne, Langres)">Lingonensis</placeName> episcopus</persName>
                        <witDetail wit="#B">Fin du texte attesté par la photographie</witDetail>,
                        notum facio presentibus et futuris quod <persName key="d1e13416" xml:id="d1e137042">Johannes de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324373" xml:id="d1e137044" corresp="Asnières-en-Montagne (Côte-d'Or, Montbard)">Asneriis</placeName>
                        </persName> dedit <lb n="2" /> et concessit Deo et fratribus ecclesie
                            <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#282689" xml:id="d1e137049" corresp="abbaye Notre-Dame de Fontenay (1119 -)">Fonteneti</orgName>
                        quicquid ad eum pertinebat de secatorio bosci <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324341" xml:id="d1e137052" corresp="Planay (Côte-d'Or, Montbard)">Plaaneti</placeName>, sic <lb n="3" /> tamen ut idem secatorium deinceps <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#282689" xml:id="d1e137058" corresp="abbaye Notre-Dame de Fontenay (1119 -)">Fontenetensibus</orgName> augere non liceat excidio
                        nemoris circun<lb n="4" break="no" />stantis, nis hoc eis ipse <persName key="d1e13422" xml:id="d1e137063">Johannes</persName> concedat vel
                        heredes ipsius. Hoc autem juraverunt super sancta filii <lb n="5" /> ejusdem
                            <persName key="d1e13428" xml:id="d1e137068">Johannis</persName>,
                            <persName key="d1e13435" xml:id="d1e137072">Rainerius</persName>,
                            <persName key="d1e13441" xml:id="d1e137075">Carpinus</persName>,
                            <persName key="d1e13447" xml:id="d1e137078">Rainaldus</persName>,
                            <persName key="d1e13453" xml:id="d1e137081">Bauduinus</persName>, quod
                        deinceps nichil suum clamabunt, <lb n="6" /> nec ipsi nec heredes ipsorum nec
                        in ipso bosco excorticabunt. Quod si quis ceterorum participum <lb n="7" />
                        corticem ibi levaverit. <persName key="d1e13459" xml:id="d1e137089">Johannes</persName> vel ipsius heredes monachos admonebunt, ut eum qui
                        levaverit <lb n="8" /> cessare faciant. Quod si cessare noluerit, et ipsi
                        similiter levabunt. Habuit propter hoc <persName key="d1e13465" xml:id="d1e137094">Johannes</persName> de bene<lb n="9" break="no" />ficio ejusdem ecclesie .XL. solidos. Hec etiam laudavit <persName key="d1e13472" xml:id="d1e137099">Uldealdis</persName> uxor ejusdem et
                        pro laude .VII. solidos <lb n="10" /> recepit. Singulis etiam annis reddent
                        monachi predicte <persName key="d1e13478" xml:id="d1e137105">Uldealdi</persName> .XII. nummos debito censua<lb n="11" break="no" />li, vel cuicumque ipsa voluerit. Horum testes sunt frater <persName key="d1e13484" xml:id="d1e137110">Hugo, magister <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324452" xml:id="d1e137112" corresp="Fontaines-en-Duesmois (Côte-d'Or, Châtillon-sur-Seine)">Fontanarum</placeName>
                        </persName>, frater <persName key="d1e13490" xml:id="d1e137115">Petrus,
                            magister <lb n="12" />
                            <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324341" xml:id="d1e137118" corresp="Planay (Côte-d'Or, Montbard)">Plaaneti</placeName>
                        </persName>, <persName key="d1e13496" xml:id="d1e137121">Hugo
                            leprosus</persName>, <persName key="d1e13502" xml:id="d1e137124">
                            <foreign>Costelez</foreign> de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324375" xml:id="d1e137128" corresp="Verdonnet (Côte-d'Or, Montbard)">Verdunniaco</placeName>
                        </persName>, <persName key="d1e13509" xml:id="d1e137132">Willelmus de
                                <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324373" xml:id="d1e137134" corresp="Asnières-en-Montagne (Côte-d'Or, Montbard)">Asneriis</placeName>
                        </persName> et <persName key="d1e13515" xml:id="d1e137137">Raaldus</persName> frater ejus, et <persName key="d1e13521" xml:id="d1e137140">Micha<lb n="13" break="no" />el</persName> nepos
                        eorum. Medietatem etiam totius territorii <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324341" xml:id="d1e137145" corresp="Planay (Côte-d'Or, Montbard)">Plaaneti</placeName>, que ad eundem <persName key="d1e13527" xml:id="d1e137148">Johannem</persName> pertinebat, hoc
                        pacto <lb n="14" /> emerunt fratres <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#282689" xml:id="d1e137154" corresp="abbaye Notre-Dame de Fontenay (1119 -)">Fonteneti</orgName> quod in illa deinceps nichil suum
                        clamabunt, nec ipse nec heredes ipsius. <lb n="15" /> Quod si forte
                        contigerit ut participes terre illius inter se dividant et aliquis illorum
                        de parte il<lb n="16" break="no" />la quam monachi a <persName key="d1e13533" xml:id="d1e137161">Johanne</persName> emerunt aliquid tulerit, ipse
                            <persName key="d1e13539" xml:id="d1e137164">Johannes</persName> vel
                        heredes ejus tantundem mona<lb n="17" break="no" />chis de sua parte
                        restituent. Hoc laudavit uxor illius <persName key="d1e13546" xml:id="d1e137170">Uldealdis</persName> et filii ejus omnes superius
                        nominati <lb n="18" /> qui etiam hoc super sanctas reliquias juraverunt.
                        Horum quoque testes sunt frater <persName key="d1e13552" xml:id="d1e137175">Hugo magister <lb n="19" />
                            <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324452" xml:id="d1e137178" corresp="Fontaines-en-Duesmois (Côte-d'Or, Châtillon-sur-Seine)">Fontanarum</placeName>
                        </persName>, frater <persName key="d1e13558" xml:id="d1e137181">Petrus
                            magister <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324341" xml:id="d1e137183" corresp="Planay (Côte-d'Or, Montbard)">Plaaneti</placeName>
                        </persName>, <persName key="d1e13564" xml:id="d1e137186">Wiardus de
                                <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#325027" xml:id="d1e137188" corresp="Saud">
                                <foreign>Saud</foreign>
                            </placeName>
                        </persName>, monachus <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#282689" xml:id="d1e137192" corresp="abbaye Notre-Dame de Fontenay (1119 -)">Fonteneti</orgName>, <persName key="d1e13570" xml:id="d1e137196">Bernardus capel<lb n="20" break="no" />lanus <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324375" xml:id="d1e137200" corresp="Verdonnet (Côte-d'Or, Montbard)">Verdunniaci</placeName>
                        </persName>, <persName key="d1e13576" xml:id="d1e137203">Willelmus de
                                <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324373" xml:id="d1e137205" corresp="Asnières-en-Montagne (Côte-d'Or, Montbard)">Asneriis</placeName>
                        </persName> et <persName key="d1e13583" xml:id="d1e137208">Raaldus</persName> frater ejus et <persName key="d1e13589" xml:id="d1e137211">Girardus</persName> filius ejusdem <persName key="d1e13595" xml:id="d1e137214">Willelmi</persName>. Presentem <lb n="21" /> igitur cartam sigilli nostri appensione munientes, sub
                        excommunicationis sententia interdicimus <lb n="22" /> ne quis fratres
                            <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#282689" xml:id="d1e137222" corresp="abbaye Notre-Dame de Fontenay (1119 -)">Fonteneti</orgName>
                        super his ullo modo molestare presumat.</p>
                
